name: Papers/BICS
tagline: Chapter for Digital Classicist BICS volume
body:
The Son of Suda On-Line (SoSOL), for the Digital Classicist supplement to the Bulletin of the Institute of Classical Studies.

The Digital Classicist 2013, edited by Stuart Dunn and Simon Mahony, BICS SUPP-122, ISBN 978-1-905670-49-9.
 
The offprint includes the preliminary pages to the volume giving the ISBN and copyright date, as well as the Table of Contents.
